/ ============================================================
/ LÓGICA DE GEOMETRÍA (Modifica aquí la forma)
/ ============================================================
CHECK_SHAPE, HEX 000
/ --- EJEMPLO: TRIÁNGULO PIRÁMIDE ---
/ Lógica: FILA - |COL - 7| >= 0
LOAD COL
SUBT MITAD
JNS ABS_VAL        / AC = |COL - 7|
STORE TMP
LOAD FILA
SUBT TMP           / AC = FILA - |COL - 7|
SKIPCOND 000       / Si es negativo, está fuera
JUMP IS_INSIDE
LOAD ZERO          / Fuera
JUMPI CHECK_SHAPE
IS_INSIDE,   LOAD ONE           / Dentro
JUMPI CHECK_SHAPE

ABS_VAL,     HEX 000            / Subrutina Valor Absoluto
SKIPCOND 000
JUMPI ABS_VAL
STORE TMP
LOAD ZERO
SUBT TMP
JUMPI ABS_VAL

/ ============================================================
/ INICIO Y MENSAJES
/ ============================================================
START,       JNS MSG_START
LOAD ZERO
STORE SCORE
JNS INIT_BOARD
JNS CALC_SAFE
JUMP RENDER

MSG_START,   HEX 000
LOAD ASC_S | OUTPUT | LOAD ASC_T | OUTPUT
LOAD ASC_A | OUTPUT | LOAD ASC_R | OUTPUT
LOAD ASC_T | OUTPUT | JUMPI MSG_START

/ ============================================================
/ BUCLE PRINCIPAL E INTERACCIÓN
/ ============================================================
MAIN_LOOP,   INPUT | STORE FILA
INPUT | STORE COL
INPUT | STORE ACCION
JNS CALC_IDX

JNS CHECK_SHAPE    / Validar click en la geometría
SKIPCOND 800
JUMP MAIN_LOOP

LOAD ACCION
SUBT ONE
SKIPCOND 400
JUMP DO_FLAG
JUMP DO_REVEAL

/ ============================================================
/ LÓGICA DE PUNTAJE (SCORE)
/ ============================================================
DO_FLAG,     JNS FLG_LOGIC
JUMP RENDER

FLG_LOGIC,   HEX 000
LOAD INDEX | ADD B_VIS | STORE DIR
LOADI DIR | STORE TMP
SUBT ST_REVEAL
SKIPCOND 400
JUMP FLG_TOGGLE
JUMPI FLG_LOGIC
FLG_TOGGLE:  LOAD TMP
SUBT ST_FLAG
SKIPCOND 400
JUMP ADD_FLG
/ Quitar Bandera
LOAD ST_HIDDEN | STOREI DIR
JNS UPD_SCORE_NEG
JUMP FLG_OUT
/ Poner Bandera
ADD_FLG:     LOAD ST_FLAG | STOREI DIR
JNS UPD_SCORE_POS
FLG_OUT:     LOAD SCORE | OUTPUT  / Ver puntaje en consola
JUMPI FLG_LOGIC

UPD_SCORE_POS: HEX 000
LOAD INDEX | ADD B_REAL | STORE TMP
LOADI TMP
SKIPCOND 000 / ¿Es mina (-1)?
JUMP INC_S
JUMPI UPD_SCORE_POS
INC_S:         LOAD SCORE | ADD ONE | STORE SCORE
JUMPI UPD_SCORE_POS

UPD_SCORE_NEG: HEX 000
LOAD INDEX | ADD B_REAL | STORE TMP
LOADI TMP
SKIPCOND 000
JUMP DEC_S
JUMPI UPD_SCORE_NEG
DEC_S:         LOAD SCORE | SUBT ONE | STORE SCORE
JUMPI UPD_SCORE_NEG

/ ============================================================
/ RENDERIZADO Y COORDENADAS
/ ============================================================
GET_COORDS,  HEX 000            / Convierte COUNT a FILA/COL
LOAD COUNT | STORE TMP
LOAD ZERO | STORE FILA
DIV_L:       LOAD TMP | SUBT SIXTEEN
SKIPCOND 000
JUMP DO_DIV
LOAD TMP | STORE COL
JUMPI GET_COORDS
DO_DIV:      STORE TMP
LOAD FILA | ADD ONE | STORE FILA
JUMP DIV_L

RENDER,      LOAD ZERO | STORE COUNT
RND_L:       LOAD COUNT | SUBT MAX_CELLS
SKIPCOND 000 | JUMP RND_E
JNS GET_COORDS
LOAD COUNT | ADD B_DISP | STORE DIR
JNS CHECK_SHAPE
SKIPCOND 800 | JUMP D_OUT
/ --- PINTAR CELDAS JUGABLES ---
/ (Insertar aquí lógica de colores C_HID, C_FLG, C_0-C_8)
JUMP RND_N
D_OUT:       LOAD C_OUT | STOREI DIR
RND_N:       LOAD COUNT | ADD ONE | STORE COUNT | JUMP RND_L
RND_E:       / Control de GAME_STATE y salto a MAIN_LOOP